      "text": "（そっか、これが琴乃ちゃんが見てる景色なんだ……）\n（みんなの期待を舞台の中心で受けるの、凄く緊張する）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(So this is how things look through Kotono-chan’s eyes…)\n(It’s nerve-wracking‚ standing at center and carrying everyone’s expectations.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
