      "text": "すみません、今のシーンがどう映ってるか\n確認してもいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me. May I confirm\nwhat that scene looks like?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
